## STEP 11 — Mobile navigation

The chat opens as a full-screen overlay (Step 7), so no changes to the
bottom navigation are needed. The chat's own `‹` back button closes it.

However, ensure the Android hardware back button and iOS swipe-back
gesture also close the chat. Add this to the chat overlay:

```tsx
useEffect(() => {
  function handlePopState() { closeFinanceChat() }
  if (activeChatGroup) {
    window.history.pushState({ chat: true }, '')
    window.addEventListener('popstate', handlePopState)
  }
  return () => window.removeEventListener('popstate', handlePopState)
}, [activeChatGroup])
```

